# Web3Forms access key — the cover form emails each new submission (name +
# birth date) to your inbox via Web3Forms. Get a free key at
# https://web3forms.com (just enter the email submissions should go to; no
# account needed).
#
# NOTE: Web3Forms' free plan requires the request to come from the browser, so
# this key is sent client-side and is therefore PUBLIC (prefix NEXT_PUBLIC_).
# That's by design — the key is safe to expose; lock it down with domain
# restrictions / spam protection in the Web3Forms dashboard.
#
# Local dev:  copy this file to ".env.local", paste your key, restart `next dev`.
# Vercel:     add NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY under Project → Settings →
#             Environment Variables, then redeploy.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=
